column5: Any suggestions for boat rentals in the Lake Simcoe are?
Blue Beacon at the Narrows pass Orillia rents.
Would also suggest blue beacon, just keep an eye on the wind forecast before you go, could be a nasty one!
There's a fellow that works out of Kontiki marina in Lefroy.Can't think of his name,but if you call the marina they should give you the details.
